家，或數日，或十數日，始殞命，人皆不知其中傷也。<br />\n<br />\n忽一日，門扃有罅縫，同被誘之女童瞥見之，歸語其父母。事遂敗露。此聲既揚，縣尉某，先拘其妾某氏訊供。諸被害家，亦争控於官，然無贓證。良璧到案，挺身長跪，抗論不撓，謂從古無此事，何得以「莫須有」之事誣陷人。<br />\n<br />\n嚴訊三日，并呼其妾質對始吐實。二十年來，被拐者共十七人，其四人尚無恙，餘十三人皆被戕。適有同鄉御史吴椿官於朝，合邑士民公札寄知椿，據以入奏皇上，飭地方有司，訊得實情，良璧照採〈生炙割律〉，凌遲處死。妾及子皆遣戍。失察之官吏，黜革有差。此嘉慶十六年八、九月間事。<br />\n<br />\n---清　趙翼《簷曝雜記》卷六"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"【注】<br />\n[0] 原標題：〈妖民吸精髓〉<br />\n[1] 徽州：算係出名地方。有興趣睇下。<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BE%BD%E5%B7%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E5%25B7%259E&d=R6lfK%2BfGLgT%2FMB3V0C5%2FP4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=7ee4aa5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BE%BD%E5%B7%9E</a><br />\n[2] 戕：即係殺。粵音「牆」。<br />\n[3] 〈生炙割律〉：自己睇。<a href=\"http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E9%87%87%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%98%E5%89%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.baike.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2587%2587%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258A%2598%25E5%2589%25B2&d=R6lfK%2BfGLgT%2FMB3V0C5%2FP4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=f52c80da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E9%87%87%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%98%E5%89%B2</a>"},{"pid":"1fbee88d921a4b0d980944cceeb2db233fdfdae7","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/124645_031265a97b2379d151f99150280807d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F124645_031265a97b2379d151f99150280807d6.jpg&h=e3753a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n徽州歙縣顏子街，有個妖人叫做張良璧，專吸細路女精髓。佢成七十幾歲人，鬍鬚眉毛白哂，但係個樣只係三四十歲。<br />\n<br />\n哩啲叔叔誘騙小朋友通常都係話睇金魚，入到房囉，就用藥吹入細路鼻孔，咁就即刻暈低啦，然後就呵呵呵呵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">做咩？</div><br />\n食肥婆要落美極，食細路女就要用飲管！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n係咁吸、係咁吸。吸完，送返屋企，通常都要過多幾日先死既。其他人就梗係唔知個女畀條仆街吸死左啦。<br />\n<br />\n有一日，張良璧又呃左幾個細路女返屋企睇金魚。當佢吸緊其中一個嗰陣，咁岩門有罅縫，未畀人吸嗰個就睇到成件事。哩個細佬醒呀，即刻鳩衝返屋企話畀老豆老母聽，然後件事就黃了。<br />\n<br />\n之後十幾家人都一齊爭住告佢啦，不過就無罪證。你會唔會話飲管係凶器先。張良璧就梗係話無啲咁既事，佢同馬時亨一樣咁有責任感，係其他人屈佢啦，「莫須有」呀。<br />\n<br />\n審左三日，捉埋老婆出黎對質先肯認。二十年內，一共捉左十七個細路女，吸死左十三個。最後張良璧就凌遲處死，妾同個仔就發配邊疆。喱件係嘉慶十六年八、九月既事，堅料黎。"},{"pid":"7c34aa084ea9b4c7a785bd730b32fb0a58d0e9b2","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:31:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f467f41f05f5dc1c87d2728c9b3fe3c6f1eee36c","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfd46662fa96eff2472de085e260f492f16a6f27","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到過左7 日，公海都仲睇到"},{"pid":"8c95cf02000a6c39fd84a8650877406418e1097f","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"推到50"},{"pid":"3b4e3678f5d704723d4b6ad3431389f1f9d4fd48","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"推到50"},{"pid":"5aae440a43a36902a697847cc4058962e5775744","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"〈尋找hehe的故事五．唔好夾硬黎〉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/170905_a87bcff583575fd941f2622e4761f133.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F170905_a87bcff583575fd941f2622e4761f133.JPG&h=d043f429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我認識的第一對BL</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王蘭洲嘗於舟次[1]買一童，年十三四，甚秀雅，亦粗知字義。云父歿，家中落，與母兄[2]投親不遇，附舟南還，行李典賣盡，故鬻身為道路費。與之語，羞澀如新婦，固已怪之。<br />\n<br />\n比[3]就寢，竟弛服橫陳，王本買供使令，無他念，然宛轉相就，亦意不自持。已而，童伏枕暗泣。<br />\n<br />\n問：「汝不願乎？」曰：「不願。」<br />\n<br />\n問：「不願何以先就我？」<br />\n<br />\n曰：「吾父在時，所畜小奴數人，無不薦枕席，有初來愧拒者，輒加鞭笤曰：『思買汝何為，憒憒[4]乃爾。知奴事主人，分當如是，不如是，則當箠楚。』故不敢不自獻也。」<br />\n<br />\n王蹶然推枕曰：「可畏哉。」急呼舟人鼓楫。一夜，追及其母兄，以童還之，且贈以五十金。意不自安，復於憫忠寺禮佛懺悔，夢伽藍語曰：「汝作過改過在頃刻間，冥司尚未注籍，可無庸瀆世尊[5]也。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 清 紀昀《閱微草堂筆記》卷六"},{"pid":"1d01b49b6181375735443b9aec2d0424db3e0b75","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"【注】<br />\n<br />\n[1] 舟次：航程，旅途之中。<br />\n<br />\n[2] 母兄：同母親的兄長。點解要咁分？以前唔係一夫一妻。<br />\n<br />\n[3] 比：副詞解「等到」。<br />\n<br />\n[4] 憒：解「心智昏亂」。<br />\n<br />\n[5] 世尊：佛陀的尊號之一。"},{"pid":"8ba7aa9364e6c8bf30d7346c6853c7be2cca1dc2","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"【錯譯】<br />\n<br />\n王蘭洲有次搭船出trip，中途買左個男仔返黎。個男仔十三、四歲，白白滑滑，識幾隻字，文青feel。個男仔話，自己老豆死左，家道中落，佢想同阿哥想投靠親戚又失敗，死返屋企既途中，成副身家賣哂出去，唯有賣埋自己賺路費。王蘭洲同佢講野，又怕醜豬豬成個小妹妹咁，呵呵呵呵。<br />\n<br />\n去到夜晚，要瞓覺覺豬了。男仔除哂衫，自己攤上王蘭洲張床。王蘭洲原本諗住買個男仔返黎當工人用，無其他諗法，點知男仔自願培瞓&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/171120_aab13c0c9730abe224cfda63c29973e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F171120_aab13c0c9730abe224cfda63c29973e9.jpg&h=12c22ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼前有個衰十一既機會，白滑的胴體、幼嫩的菊花&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呵呵呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n完事之後，男仔攬住枕頭喊。<br />\n<br />\n王蘭洲問：「你唔係想咩？」男仔答：「唔想。」<br />\n<br />\n王蘭洲問：「唔想，咁你除哂衫上我張床做咩？」<br />\n<br />\n男仔答：「以前我老豆，都養左幾個男仔，全部都要培瞓。有啲新黎唔肯培既，老豆就會鞭打佢話：『你諗下我買你返黎做咩？你都戇鳩。做工人服侍主人，就應該要培瞓。唔培瞓，就要SM。』所以我唔敢唔培瞓。」<br />\n<br />\n王蘭洲聽完就嚇到彈起身：「我真係仆街囉。」拿拿臨叫船夫轉頭。一晚，追到去佢大佬度，還返個男仔畀佢，仲送多五十金。之後仲係覺得唔安心，走左去間佛寺懺悔。有次夢見伽藍神話：「你做錯同改過都係幾秒鐘既事，地府閻羅mark 唔切，哩單衰十一就唔同你計啦。」"},{"pid":"b96fe99627ef4c9bef2515cb6364d30a2f9ec13c","tid":749578,"uid":190601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解學術台轆極都搵唔到呢個post"},{"pid":"266fdde34dcf5267d5a3a807370f56cb5f004e46","tid":749578,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ec061fd1752a7e846c299171b95d914be06f76","tid":749578,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdb69486f593642c909fe96a5a15d0d4e0461930","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96fe99627ef4c9bef2515cb6364d30a2f9ec13c","tid":749578,"uid":190601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解學術台轆極都搵唔到呢個post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"我都成日都搵唔到自己個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3630dfea8f82f26af0f04ddc36a0bb8fda40bdd6","tid":749578,"uid":190601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb69486f593642c909fe96a5a15d0d4e0461930","tid":749578,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96fe99627ef4c9bef2515cb6364d30a2f9ec13c","tid":749578,"uid":190601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\